Why do we need GIT?
Manage our versions locally on our computer

What is GIT?
version control tool, local repository

What is github?
remote repository

Revision
TRacking our first project using GIT
scenario: work on a project and maintain the version locally as well as on github

Approach:
--Tracking our very first project
1-Choose the location where you want to create the repo--> create the repo inside your working directory
Note: make sure you don't have any sub-repos (repo inside a repo)
2-navigate the terminal to the right location
